{"tid":1758234,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"區選完後應做的事","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T03:34:17.000Z","uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"676a4666246020ed5bac373d69e1fe1800a648e5","tid":1758234,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"各位，<br />\n<br />\n區選完成後，我哋要面對立法會選舉大陸在各方面的反擊。<br />\n和理非要繼續做以下事情:<br />\n1. 連攏場要繼續努力，把有關問題顯示出比街坊睇到。<br />\n2. 有收入既人，希望繼續在屋企做，比錢轉台，令家人不看CCTVB. 令長者轉過來我們這邊。<br />\n3. 希望大家如可以在每周抽些時間出來，做泛民義工，令自已所屬區變成深黃。<br />\n4. 如果可以，多點與身邊淺藍討論有關事情，我們要多一點支持。關心一下年紀大的朋友。"},{"pid":"7056e12e81be912c238fc76ee1f8da17551bf9a8","tid":1758234,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93eb8b9e90448f9577808c84eb62a60093c4eb90","tid":1758234,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"2d973a30ccf5fcc9e45c06f30c7c8f2d096c443f","tid":1758234,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fbc2a145fe90a5e7359300dafacd361629b16a3","tid":1758234,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"。ok 強推"},{"pid":"129db350100282662b760158c2389fbfc35ecc2e","tid":1758234,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019